title: BRAND NEW 1BED/1BATH IN PILSEN
posting_body: ['This gorgeous 1bed 1 bath is freshly new are ready for YOU!!', 'Located in the heart of Chicago, the renovated unit has a brand new oven, stove, refrigerator, and an in-unit washer/dryer!', 'The grey hardwood floors compliment the stunning white cabinetry.', 'The soft-grey walls tie it all in & large windows provide plenty of natural light to complement the interior.', 'This property is located in an ideal area of Chicago.', 'The unit is a 4-minute drive to the I-90 W/I-94 W highway and a 4 minute walk (0.2 miles) to the Red Line CTA stop.', 'All qualified candidates must have:', '-Credit score of 600 and a steady monthly income.(or co-signer)', '-No prior evictions or collections with Utility Companies', '-First month rent is due at lease signing', '-Move in fee of $325', '-$30 application fee', '-Pets under 35 pounds are welcomed, max 2.', 'Restrictions apply.', '1st pet free', 'This unit is beautiful and ready for great qualified tenants.', 'If you would like to schedule a viewing contact Sandy at 8479702541 by TEXT']
